1
00:00:02,750 --> 00:00:05,250
Welcome to the Handmade Market. I'm your host, Xiao Lin.

2
00:00:05,350 --> 00:00:08,050
Today we have over 50 independent handmade artisans

3
00:00:08,150 --> 00:00:10,550
with us here today.

4
00:00:10,750 --> 00:00:13,250
From pottery to weaving to leather goods—

5
00:00:13,350 --> 00:00:18,050
we have everything you could imagine.

6
00:00:18,250 --> 00:00:20,750
Let's interview a pottery vendor—

7
00:00:20,850 --> 00:00:23,350
his teacups are really popular

8
00:00:23,450 --> 00:00:25,950
his teacups are really popular
among young people.

9
00:00:26,150 --> 00:00:28,650
Hi everyone, I'm A-Ming

10
00:00:28,750 --> 00:00:31,250
from Jingdezhen.

11
00:00:31,350 --> 00:00:33,850
I've been making pottery for 8 years now.

12
00:00:34,050 --> 00:00:36,550
Every piece is hand-thrown

13
00:00:36,650 --> 00:00:39,150
and hand-glazed.

14
00:00:39,250 --> 00:00:41,750
So no two pieces are exactly the same.

15
00:00:41,950 --> 00:00:44,450
That's the charm of handmade—

16
00:00:44,550 --> 00:00:47,050
→ Hurry to booth A12

17
00:00:47,150 --> 00:00:49,650
if you want one.

18
00:00:49,750 --> 00:00:58,100
We've prepared 100 limited gifts.

19
00:00:58,250 --> 00:01:00,750
First come, first served.

20
01:05:13,150 --> 01:05:15,650
As the sky darkens, the market is wrapping up.

21
01:05:15,850 --> 01:05:18,350
Thank you so much for your support.

22
01:05:18,550 --> 01:05:21,050
See you next time!
